{"id":"76537b791c227761c03d07bc5adf296df2835f2944155bd332a9484555045d68","item_id":"2e1e21757a:0","text":"计算几何体的朝向比：即摄像机向量或方向与表面法线之间的简单点积。请注意，某些场景实体没有已定义法线，例如体积。"}
{"id":"cf64acc00597b9ee77b325323acf4007334f631da5243bcb4846582f8a2a036f","item_id":"2e1e21757a:3","text":"选择渲染摄像机方向或一个预定义方向"}
{"id":"8fffbf998c267a6b3423d22a8f62ae22c815fd0e97f647d3613a3da079fdc5b9","item_id":"2e1e21757a:5","text":"不使用摄像机方向时，在此提供方向向量"}
{"id":"b514ebf73921fea11670ca9640e96c27bc4e980867839d368eca5bd872bd174f","item_id":"2e1e21757a:6","text":"Coordinate System"}
{"id":"3865b10e6b1ff7f450e2bde2d4abde15d22af469585d385fb7437767730ca797","item_id":"2e1e21757a:7","text":"提供一个有用的坐标系统：object、world、camera 或其他已定义空间。"}
{"id":"0a4704d83834d932708f3525dec1799cd2c90fbbb78aa06c678fa399ef338d2a","item_id":"2e1e21757a:8","text":"Face Forward"}
{"id":"39c7d947494fc00c323f0bb1ec262eef53d87c22706bc7ede0ed35453fb8ba92","item_id":"2e1e21757a:9","text":"如果法线背向摄像机，朝向比可能为负。此选项会翻转法线，使结果始终为正。"}
{"id":"2920e1247e929dd1e7d3f65d36fa1f7f43d95e846f1a69a200078d32989e3776","item_id":"2e1e21757a:11","text":"将结果 Clamp（钳制）到 0 到 1 范围"}
{"id":"7e04f2ffb9334e3d19a15c949a73818d4b271b0e713dbfad612b29491b46bc1b","item_id":"2e1e21757a:12","text":"Invert"}
{"id":"b7157e71d0a693553cb74a4946afa427c9252e9c140ade74712577113ff9e26a","item_id":"2e1e21757a:13","text":"反转朝向比：黑色变为白色，白色反之变为黑色。"}
{"id":"5e23ec6a300dc60a79641769017e16e9bf042cbd8fd0a54586a048ab9da972ff","item_id":"2e1e21757a:14","text":"Mode"}
{"id":"629c10facb887417796939de295f39f7533e8b2a140380950c1b432c01f38ca3","item_id":"2e1e21757a:15","text":"选择指定 Ior 还是 Gamma"}
{"id":"1024f840d8ddb7a7b4264bde73918cb17c7af991cc5998e9db34a8aaafc30b3b","item_id":"2e1e21757a:16","text":"Ior"}
{"id":"2c5d23b63363e447a8a77a75d37a28bd2d413255274f354a73777e77faa1f943","item_id":"2e1e21757a:17","text":"使用上方设置的 Ior 模式时，选择一个折射率值，通常为 1.0 到 3.0，可用于模拟电介质表面。"}
{"id":"3b0c5bc23ccd0ce07c0a4265b0dd42d202582c08e2e62673e7dd968c04e6e1bd","item_id":"2e1e21757a:19","text":"使用上方设置的 gamma 节点时，通过一个简单的 gamma 函数塑造朝向比。值 1.0 为中性"}
{"id":"7c32d683cd2d5a3475221356783bc1194f4616ce71aff03fdf852f2330349d6c","item_id":"2e1e21757a:21","text":"如果表面应用了 bump mapping，请在此输入凹凸法线。如果未连接，节点会使用此着色法线。"}
{"id":"20cee54d3870761a41a354946a213694c0612e819dc7d1e21f529a8e727fb539","item_id":"2e1e21757a:23","text":"resultF"}
{"id":"ee1e92760c7c7825ec3737485fb9c0f46700d1d941ea79520e079702e7050146","item_id":"2e1e21757a:24","text":"由朝向比计算产生的单分量（float）值。"}
{"id":"8b76e2df9050f924b018cff8809cbc580f39a71664984ae54adf99defe9eaa2e","text":"Output Parameters（输出参数）"}
{"id": "e8756d05615a8b9aac2d138a9ae82553f3231ff237868a66679a30001b4f326b", "item_id": "2e1e21757a:1", "text": "Input Parameters（输入参数）"}
{"id": "c36d819e7bc6d2b7da51394411c733db89c395987885ca6770167a3b9bc45c3c", "item_id": "2e1e21757a:2", "text": "使用"}
{"id": "9c8a9579abe55bdc8a7b97031705e2738d912de38a35262863d8f47e05d3d641", "item_id": "2e1e21757a:4", "text": "Direction"}
{"id": "3bc5f4682203da7cee38bdb177ccc865b1c296c2cae67d883c8187a646d761a1", "item_id": "2e1e21757a:10", "text": "Clamp"}
{"id": "a8ab3d5805c9214bc66b794f599cbccd5a5958dc5a6a322ee81e3a68344c6db7", "item_id": "2e1e21757a:18", "text": "Gamma"}
{"id": "0831c68d0b80eb0844b8ebb84a1bc29b9423212e5eb46f2a1825cc4c077661f9", "item_id": "2e1e21757a:20", "text": "Bump Normal"}
